## 1. DESIGN SYSTEM & TOKENS
### A. Typography Hierarchy
- **Headline (H2):** Helvetica Neue Light | 56px | 1.1 Line-height | Letter-spacing: -0.02em.
- **Section Title (H3):** Helvetica Neue Light | 32px | 1.2 Line-height | Margin-bottom: 0.25em.
- **Body Copy (Normal):** Helvetica Neue Light | 20px | 1.7 Line-height | Color: rgba(0,0,0,0.8) | Letter-spacing: 0.5px.
- **Strategic Signature:** Helvetica Neue Regular | 12px | Color: rgba(0,0,0,0.8) | Letter-spacing: 0.1em.

### B. Spacing & Pacing (Vertical Rhythm)
- **Slide Padding:** 80px (all sides).
- **Narrative Pause (Divider):** 1px height | Solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05) | Margin: 4em 0.
- **Content Blocks:** Margin-bottom: 3em.

### C. Color Palette (Solid Grey Hex Values Only)
- **Primary:** #000000 (Titles, Buttons, Sidebar).
- **Secondary:** #FFFFFF (Background).
- **Tones:** #F9F9F9 (Cards, Background Accents).
- **Text:** rgba(0,0,0,0.8) (Standard Body).
- **Labels:** rgba(0,0,0,0.3) (Metadata).

